snippet.title: Rockman.EXE Operation Shooting Star - The Fateful Encounter
snippet.description:
It's actually comprised of four separate clips put together for all of
you with the third being a boss battle (sort of) and the fourth is the
first encounter with Hikari Netto and Hoshiwara Subaru aka Shooting
Star Rockman.
